# .roadmap.axis_bio_evolution_exploration

작성: 2026-05-08
구동: 사용자 directive — 6th axis BIO-EVOLUTION 추가 가능성 탐색 (현재 5-axis: QUANTUM / WEAVE / VIROCAPSID / RIBOZYME / NANOBOT)

본 file 은 axis-exploration meta-roadmap. BIO-EVOLUTION 을 hexa-bio 의 6th axis 로 incorporate 할 가치 + scope + cross-axis 중복도 + falsifier inventory 의 한 장 검토. 결정은 user 에게 reserved — 본 entry 는 evidence-table + raw#10 honest C3 분석 제공.

(Distinct from 기존 5 axis: BIO-EVOLUTION = nature-derived evolutionary mechanism (extremophile / animal-derived bio-source / directed evolution / synthetic minimal genome / xenobiology) 를 drug discovery primitive 로 통합. QUANTUM 은 in-silico binding, WEAVE 는 design, VIROCAPSID/RIBOZYME/NANOBOT 은 delivery — BIO-EVOLUTION 은 source library + fitness landscape exploration.)

scope:
- extremophile-derived enzyme (thermus aquaticus Taq / Pyrococcus / hyperthermophile)
- tardigrade Dsup / suspension protein (radiation + desiccation resistance)
- naked mole rat HMW hyaluronan + cancer resistance
- horseshoe crab LAL (Limulus amebocyte lysate) endotoxin assay
- cone snail conotoxin (ω-conotoxin / ziconotide-Prialt 2004 FDA)
- xenotransplantation pig gene editing (10-gene CRISPR-pig / eGenesis 2024)
- directed evolution antibody + enzyme library (Frances Arnold 2018 Nobel)
- cell-free protein synthesis (CFPS — PURE / E. coli S30)
- synthetic minimal genome (JCVI-syn3.0 — 473 gene 2016 Venter)
- xenobiology — XNA (HNA / TNA / GNA) + non-canonical amino acid (ncAA)
- ancient gene resurrection (paleo-genomics + reconstructed enzyme)
- 한국 산업 — 셀트리온 antibody / 한미 LAPS / GC녹십자 anti-toxin

