## 3. Falsifier inventory (entry skeleton, F-axis-bioevol-*-N)

- **F-axis-bioevol-extr-1**: extremophile-derived enzyme stability vs mesophile baseline (Tm + half-life)
- **F-axis-bioevol-anim-1**: conotoxin library 의 ion-channel selectivity ranking via QUANTUM-VQE
- **F-axis-bioevol-anim-2**: xenotransplant pig 10-gene editing 의 hyperacute rejection 회피 (PERV-KO + GTKO + complement KO)
- **F-axis-bioevol-de-1**: directed-evolution + Codexis-style biocatalysis 가 wild-type 대비 ≥10x rate enhancement
- **F-axis-bioevol-de-2**: phage-display antibody library 의 binding affinity ≥1nM 후보 enrichment ratio
- **F-axis-bioevol-syn-1**: JCVI-syn3.0 chassis 의 drug-production yield vs E. coli BL21 baseline
- **F-axis-bioevol-xeno-1**: XNA aptamer 의 nuclease resistance + binding retention (HNA / TNA)
- **F-axis-bioevol-xeno-2**: ncAA-incorporated ADC 의 site-specificity (DAR uniformity ≥0.9)
- **F-axis-bioevol-cfps-1**: cell-free protein synthesis (CFPS) 의 yield + folding fidelity vs in-vivo baseline
- **F-axis-bioevol-cross-1**: BIO-EVOL × QUANTUM cross — bio-derived 분자 pool 의 VQE binding ranking
- **F-axis-bioevol-cross-2**: BIO-EVOL × WEAVE cross — directed-evol 결과를 WEAVE composition 입력으로
- **F-axis-bioevol-redundancy-1**: BIO-EVOL 의 falsifier 중 ≥30% 가 기존 5-axis 와 substantive duplicate 면 axis 추가 reject (meta-falsifier)

